SUMMARY:Intermediate Ride (C) - EP Landisville Casual (22F)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n**Be Safe\, Have Fun\, an
 d Ride Together**\n\nRide leader: open\nAnticipated Average Pace: (14-16 m
 ph)\nRoute: [https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/ep-landisville-casua
 l-ride-22f/](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/ep-landisville-casua
 l-ride-22f/)\n\nThis is an Intermediate C Class ride. The ride leader will
  ride at the advertised average speed. This is intended to be a group ride
  with a no-drop rule as the main goal. The ride leader will do his/her bes
 t to keep the group together with occasional regroupings and/or splitting 
 into multiple groups to align to pace capabilities.\n\nPlease do not join 
 this ride if you are not willing to ride with the group. If you exceed the
  posted pace\, you will be riding by yourself and encouraged to join a fas
 ter group. If maintaining a 14-16 mph average is beyond your current abili
 ty level\, please consider joining a slower ride first.\n\nHelmets are man
 datory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\
 , tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen a
 nd paper waiver\, we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to 
 join this ride. Being on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. Join 
 here [Member Signup](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_i
 d=60&club_id=257148)\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's
  Code of Conduct: [Code of Conduct](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/cont
 ent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\n\nGuidance if an inc
 ident occurs: [Incident Actions](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/content.asp
 x?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=326137)
