SUMMARY:Virtual Ride Leader Training
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nVirtual training session 
 for becoming a Ride Leader. If you select attend\, I will email a meeting 
 invite and a pre-read packet of information.\n\nThank you for volunteering
  to be a ride leader! Ride leaders are an important part of helping us ach
 ieve our priorities of being safe\, having fun\, and riding together. Apar
 t from making rides an enjoyable experience for everyone\, ride leaders pi
 ck ride times\, locations\, routes\, and social events\, if interested. Th
 ey also receive cycling swag through the Ride Hero program that provides g
 ift certificates or cycling jerseys for every 10 rides you lead.
